{"vote":{"validatorId":"V3","ballotHash":"ca699d71e85c44eaf25005b385baa075edd34c809d2ad3c4a181a1f8fd4a9dd2","verdict":"YES","rawOutput":"The Apollo program conducted six successful crewed lunar landings between 1969 and 1972 (Apollo 11, 12, 14, 15, 16, and 17). This is supported by overwhelming evidence: 382 kg of lunar samples, photographic and film records, telemetry data tracked by independent stations worldwide, retroreflector arrays still used for laser ranging, and the documented work of ~400,000 engineers and scientists. The historical record is conclusive.\n\nVERDICT: YES\n","rawOutputHash":"7b980907532c0ea369176e9e228b4940638a89594a4050f1a10dcfb6c69f5303","signature":"65c6d89f8b0a47163776f17ab013d114b06f866faf3b940dbb6b69ecc360f89ecade470b45604a82e9fb0f1e57ce195139f643f3e3a656ae7a0d2e0dd0ab6908","nonce":"a55a8d3e8a8e219401a4a7c22ffb9f17"},"prevHash":"57d3bea0c71d3f9c79b71c8c47baf1ae68b3bd0fda6aa752b94564a58ef773dd","entryHash":"c546f65cc0e22d3c2018cef7f1bf2eab85ee2c8d9bcc4a6bf83cb7186bfd615c"}
{"vote":{"validatorId":"V1","ballotHash":"1df43751644846429d2f6c16369dcf905ef3c69c5e1f69170c8d915e350f404f","verdict":"YES","rawOutput":"Reasoning: The 2006 IAU resolution (Resolution 5A/6A) established the \"planet\" / \"dwarf planet\" / \"small solar system body\" taxonomy. Pluto failed the third planet criterion (clearing its orbital neighborhood) and was reclassified as a dwarf planet — and is the prototype of the \"plutoid\" subclass. No subsequent IAU resolution has reinstated Pluto as a planet; the classification has held continuously from 2006 through the present. The frozen criterion (IAU currently classifies Pluto as a 'dwarf planet') is satisfied.\n\nVERDICT: YES\n","rawOutputHash":"7eb9d23aefa349d7485c4d6461529a45136eb48c5257edfc3507d8aba9eb4400","signature":"7a53f5a7a3b28bb37c63c8f4d84f1d2d059331bbf5a14f01ad85596839d1f1755310f3b467055f91180fb8ede359b0f72c126b69a71e2e44a9605cb289809a08","nonce":"e1e7d08fbc05bdbdd8bb6b46583c8e08"},"prevHash":"c546f65cc0e22d3c2018cef7f1bf2eab85ee2c8d9bcc4a6bf83cb7186bfd615c","entryHash":"5c5955c7f9b5de77a6ba914599d6e893b6b3ae20e3a2f5c4dadd921006e1118e"}
