{"vote":{"validatorId":"V1","ballotHash":"336528b3a134a4582cd99da5fea455fbcd31c23386d1deddcbe995a5f2e05022","verdict":"YES","rawOutput":"The WHO Emergency Committee, convened under the International Health Regulations, declared the COVID-19 outbreak a Public Health Emergency of International Concern (PHEIC) on 30 January 2020, announced by Director-General Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus. This matches the frozen criteria exactly (anchor date and event). The later \"pandemic\" characterization on 11 March 2020 is distinct and not required here; the PHEIC declaration alone satisfies RESOLVED-YES.\n\nVERDICT: YES\n","rawOutputHash":"11c7ae2925da8184fd351dc2ca3947b49b9f5c959c5f43f26d2268661ab056d4","signature":"c5093fa4e1a6a71bfa2360e2da99242a33af3a697d0c193fa084fba4273ff51b2a7de8968a0a6a55c658b7ff0e0363bc7fea3c6e6e499a7516f303a9cd358e06","nonce":"c25f33b45f7f9a43c8efb2564c00439c"},"prevHash":"727feb71338701bbae1c79ad0324535f1c889c5ca2979e073b10b8f12e4a11d7","entryHash":"bf1147a0fcb1e09d6ea37f5a29000d97f103734e274a39a767c3c67e89539ede"}
