{"vote":{"validatorId":"V3","ballotHash":"e9e235fc602b804d9d57df5e51406b947404f7958b8a79abc5f11b6c64f27d05","verdict":"YES","rawOutput":"Ethereum's transition from proof-of-work to proof-of-stake via \"The Merge\" is one of the most extensively documented events in cryptocurrency history. The upgrade occurred on September 15, 2022 (block 15,537,394 on the execution layer),当 the Beacon Chain (which had been running PoS since December 2020) was merged with the existing PoW mainnet. This eliminated energy-intensive mining and replaced it with validator-based consensus. The event was verified by every node operator, major exchange, block explorer, and the broader blockchain community. There is no credible dispute about this fact.\n\nVERDICT: YES\n","rawOutputHash":"888cfe2be06c6143e9f0339f62abaccd3bf98794f7ac95d07c2256d7ce29a597","signature":"d37e6b0c888a2e92b6bf39deee431a012f592e9d58abf978a218b9cb08f1aee2202fb70ab5bdb746b83d02bfc8d03eed618c7f480161a435aa0ce94db661bf08","nonce":"c041350a3e22f525734a609ff34a1f21"},"prevHash":"f03a1bd5649d19748ced3b36d49195fe308cf88312c0c374ca4f43627d4a6c5c","entryHash":"9b9ef8f4e01cb3d5a96a0f6af22dbe54f478a38927d5d211f51b632f274139cb"}
