{"vote":{"validatorId":"V1","ballotHash":"7d2d9d18650c3aab80fd5f4478956ceef73f940445b4e3355323c49aca01b78f","verdict":"YES","rawOutput":"ChatGPT launched November 30, 2022. In early February 2023, Reuters reported a UBS study (based on Similarweb data) estimating ChatGPT reached ~100 million monthly active users in January 2023 — roughly two months post-launch — and described it as the fastest-growing consumer application in history.\n\nThis matches the frozen criteria precisely: ~100M MAU within about two months (by ~Jan 2023), supported by contemporaneous analyst estimates and widespread reporting. The estimate was an analyst projection (not an official OpenAI metric), but the criteria explicitly anchor on contemporaneous reporting/analyst estimates, which is exactly what exists.\n\nVERDICT: YES\n","rawOutputHash":"bcfa95bc492f0ca218e112a819c16f46c35447724418559c4f1f30a8a207ed18","signature":"3a560fe928a8fb78fc84ec99420f9a2da3aa3bb9bfd79d4bea05ba8bc869504a5f6aeae82cdafdfea1dce0883283e2e1e61509c682a853c1ea7c57954602f40a","nonce":"0e9428ce3e37546c2a7919dab89ec315"},"prevHash":"ee3d34b6e04391afc34c98964e914882843ac9f7dcd4cd3f85ceaf6c39dbfcca","entryHash":"1c8b82e49eac00dab3a6b4be8ff1b7595e32ba202b278450c2669e603af12d11"}
